summary: This is a cover email transmitting two final memos from the United States Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York to the Deputy Attorney General regarding cases, likely related to the Epstein investigation. The subject line suggests it concerns recusal matters.
keyFacts: Two final memos were sent from the SDNY USAO to the Deputy Attorney General on May 23, 2019.
The subject line indicates the memos concern 'GSB' cases and a recusal matter.
The document is a cover email transmitting the attached memos, which are not included in the provided text.
